 @@ -64,6 +64,8 @@  %{_libexecdir}/awk/grcat
  %{_libexecdir}/awk/pwcat
 +%{_infodir}/*
 +%{_mandir}/man1/pm-gawk.1.gz
```

This explicitly packages all unpackaged info files and the `pm-gawk` man page, satisfying RPM's unpackaged file check. No other changes are required.
